Description: GUI for MS SSO OpenConnect VPN client
 A graphical user interface for connecting to VPNs that use
 Microsoft Single Sign-On authentication, supporting both
 Cisco AnyConnect and GlobalProtect protocols.
 .
 Features:
  - System tray icon with real-time connection status
  - Multiple VPN connection profiles
  - Automatic TOTP code generation
  - Session cookie caching for fast reconnection
  - Support for both Cisco AnyConnect and GlobalProtect VPNs
